name: Nobody
description:
Jburn x SpaceLab collab

Produced by Riddiman
Cover Art/Gif by SpaceLab

Lyrics:
I am not chosen, I'm just a man moment hoping to own it, voice of the hopeless, living the life of the broken, showing the showless, anything goes when everything's open source is so potent what is he smoking call me a joke but call me again when you need me I know its the way that goes I'm really not going, I'm really so stuck in my ways I'm keeping my pace and holding my space avoiding the fake but you cant relate, I'm right and you know it, I shine like I'm golden, but light cant reflect off my skin if I clothe it, so I'm naked and showing, anything everything all of me I will expose it.
